snippet.title: Así es cómo Amber Heard sacará provecho de su triunfo en juicio contra Depp
snippet.description: La actriz de 34 años ha sido firmada por una asociación que busca dar voz a los derechos de las mujeres. Aunque una parte de la pelea entre Johnny Depp y Amber Heard concluyó hace unas semanas (al menos ante los tribunales), todo parece indicar que el tema seguirá dando de qué hablar. Pues ahora, se dio a conocer que la actriz de 34 años sacará provecho a las experiencias que vivió mientras estuvo casa con Depp. Fue en este 2020 cuando Johnny y Amber se vieron nuevamente en los tribunales de Londres, donde se llevó a cabo el juicio por la demanda que el actor interpuso contra el diario The Sun, luego de haber sido llamado ‘golpeador de esposas, misma que perdió y le costó su papel en la saga ‘Animales fantásticos’, spin-off de Harry Potter. Pero mientras Johnny tuvo ese pequeño tropiezo en su carrera, a Amber parece haberle beneficiado su triunfo sobre el equipo legal del actor, pues según informes de Dayli Mail, la actriz está en pláticas con una asociación para realizar conferencias.

snippet.title: Amber Rose - Fame (feat. Wiz Khalifa)
snippet.description:
Download link: http://ul.to/j51kj67p (MP3 format, 7 MB). 

LYRICS:

Scrutinized,
Being blind sided by all the lights
They question what I'm made of
Like these rumours weren't made up
Can't shop for clothes, or buy some cigs
Without paparazzi waiting for a flick
This is a new situation
Now you're an overnight sensation

You're not ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh
You're not ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh

Can't deny, it's just fly
Private jets, flying high
Rocking, rocking things you won't see
Tell 'em made by givenchy
Three years ago, just a girl
Now your name is known around the world
This is a new situation
Now you're an overnight sensation

Now you're ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh
Now you're ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh

[Wiz Khalifa]
Uh, and you made it, this year,
Coming up so they hate it
Fly first class so the could get mad
You heard what they have to say but you paid it,
Now you're busting out
Doing your thing, in your face, cuss 'em out
Brag cause you're the one that they fuss about
You's bad little, motha shut your mouth cause

(everything you say will and can be used against you)

It's all because of the fame
F.A.M.E (repeats)

[Chorus]
Now you're ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh
Now you're ready for the fame
Woah oh oh oh

F.A.M.E (repeats)

Amber Rose's first single is here for you to pass judgement on. We'll tell you right off the bat it's probably something you didn't expect. Over a upbeat, piano driven instrumental, Wiz's boo sings about her life in the public eye. Instead of firing back at the critics, the bald beauty explains her journey to  the limelight. I'm sure folks will focus on the fact they can keep up with the beat so, by industry standards, that makes this an okay song.  As for her vocal ability, we can't really tell when there's auto-tune and production masking it. 

Amber said she's taking vocal lessons:
"I have my own unique sound, I make music that I love and I hope that my fans and the people that embrace me will love it also!  I've taken vocal lessons and I'm working on my album, but right now I'm in the beginning phases and I'm just taking my time."

Depuis quelques jours maintenant, les témoins se succèdent à la Cour royale de justice de Londres et livrent une toute autre version des faits.  Ce vendredi 17 juillet, c'était au tour d'Isaac Baruch, voisin et ami de l'acteur, de témoigner. À ce moment, Johnny Depp lui aurait alors confié qu'Amber Heard aimait "se disputer et frapper".  Incrédul ...

snippet.title: Johnny Depp ha detto sì, nozze con Amber Heard a Los Angeles
snippet.description:
Roma, (askanews) - Johnny Depp si è sposato. Le voci sul matrimonio con la fidanzata attrice Amber Heard, a cui è legato dal 2012, si rincorrevano da mesi e l'attore dei "Pirati dei caraibi" è riuscito a mantenere quasi tutto segreto fino all'ultimo, convolando a nozze con una cerimonia civile low profile, come riporta la stampa locale, il 3 febbraio nella villa di Los Angeles dell'attore, nel quartiere di West Hollywood.
Depp, 51 anni, e la sua compagna bionda di 28, si sono conosciuti nel 2011 sul set del film "The Rum Diary" e da allora sono diventati inseparabili. Ma il loro amore è stato reso pubblico solo dopo che il divo ha annunciato la fine della sua lunga relazione con Vanessa Paradis, da cui ha avuto due figli.
Per l'eclettico interprete di Jack Sparrow quello con Amber è il secondo matrimonio. Prima della lunga love story con l'attrice e cantante francese Paradis, è stato sposato per due anni con la make up artist Lori Anne Allison.

snippet.title: Comedy - SYRUP - TRAILER | Amber Heard, Shiloh Fernandez, Kellan Lutz
snippet.description:
Based on the best-selling book, SYRUP is an edgy comedy that exposes the cut-throat world of advertising through the eyes of a young prodigy chasing fame, fortune, and the woman of his dreams. Fresh out of school with a degree in marketing, Scat will do anything to prove that he has what it takes to swim with the rich and wildly successful. Scat comes up with a brilliant new product that gives new meaning to the old saying "sex sells." He is sure it will send him right to the top...if only he can convince his boss, the beautiful and mysterious "6," that it's an idea worth millions. Betrayed by his best friend "Sneaky Pete," Scat stumbles through an industry riddled with deception. As he begins to realize that fame and fortune have cost him his morality, he must rediscover his true self behind the elaborate image he has created or risk losing the love of his life.

snippet.title: Amber Heard ¿Se niega a declarar?
snippet.description:
La novela por entregas en la que se está convirtiendo el juicio por violencia doméstica de Amber Heard contra Johnny Depp, sigue dando de qué hablar.

Los abogados de Depp pidieron que Amber declarara ante el juez el Jueves por la tarde, pero ella, a través de sus apoderados informó a la corte que no podría hacerlo, ya que tenía que ir a Londres para las pruebas de vestuario de La Liga de la Justicia y solo podría regresar a Los  Angeles el jueves por la noche que era la fecha pactada para la audiencia.

El juez aceptó los argumentos de la actriz, pero el portal TMZ sorprendió a Amber conduciendo su vehículo por las calles de Los Angeles el Miércoles, con lo que la actriz nunca fue a Londres. Los abogados de Amber dicen que ella no les informó de ello mientras que los de Johnny Depp dicen que todo es mentira.

Amber ha dicho que la prueba de vestuario fue pospuesta debido a que está muy flaca y ha perdido casi 10 kilos de peso, debido al stress.

Los abogados de Johnny Depp han dejado caer que Amber tiene temor de declarar ante el juez bajo juramento y someterse a nuevas pruebas.

Seguro que hay un próximo capítulo
-----------------------------------
Visítenos en www.celebmas.com

snippet.description:
Syrup directed by Aram Rappaport and starring Shiloh Fernandez, Amber Heard

Synopsis:
Fresh out of school with a degree in marketing, Scat will do anything to prove that he has what it takes to swim with the rich and wildly successful. He comes up with a brilliant new product that gives new 
meaning to the old saying "sex sells" and is sure it will send him right to the top...if only he can convince his boss, the beautiful and mysterious "6," that it's an idea worth millions. Betrayed by his best 
friend, Scat stumbles through an industry riddled with deception. As he begins to realize that fame and fortune have cost him his morality, he must rediscover his true self behind the elaborate image he has created or risk losing the love of his life.

Release Date: June 7th, 2013
Genre: Comedy
Cast: Shiloh Fernandez, Amber Heard and Kellan Lutz
Directors: Aram Rappaport

snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Bahamas Beach Wedding
snippet.description:
Bahamas Beach Wedding: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Bahamas Beach Wedding - http://www.bahamas-destination-wedding.com/AskGlenn

Hi I'm Glenn Ferguson, wedding officiant in Nassau Bahamas with another spotlight on weddings in the Bahamas. Today we're featuring  Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Bahamas Beach Wedding. 

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard chose a Bahamian island for their wedding earlier this month. The wedding was held on Little Hall’s Pond Cay, the private island owned by Depp in the Exuma Island chain.

Depp first purchased the island 11 years ago, after he first filmed Pirates of the Caribbean in the Bahamas. The 45-acre island has six private beaches and Depp is among the latest celebrities to get married in the Bahamas.

Take a look at the video and see the beauty that Johnny and Amber enjoyed at their beach wedding in the Bahamas.

And you have have questions about planning a Bahamas Beach wedding call me Glenn Ferguson, wedding officiant Nassau Bahamas at 1-(242)-327-2453 and I'll get you the help you need to experience your Beach wedding in the Bahamas.
